snippet.title: DILUVIAN WINDS - Project presentation
snippet.description:
WISHLIST ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1561040?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=announcement

Diluvian Winds is a sail-punk simulation game in a context of exile due to the rising waters. Survive as you expand your community in your lighthouse.

Diluvian Winds is coming to PC and Nintendo Switch in 2022.

Follow us on social media:
➤ Discord: https://discord.gg/sVrGeamFVc
➤ Twitter: https://twitter.com/AlambikStudio
➤ Steam Publisher Page: https://store.steampowered.com/franchise/goblinz_publishing
